'''Nickel One''' was a large asteroid in the [[Roche asteroid field|Roche asteroid belt]] and the capital of the [[Roche system]], home of the [[Verpine/Legends|Verpine]] [[Species/Legends|species]].

==History==
Following the end of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], Nickel One became the adopted [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] for the Verpine. There, they maintained their primary munitions factories.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

During the [[Swarm War]], Nickel One was attacked by a convoy of [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] vessels, though [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]], along with [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]], were able to repulse the invaders.<ref name="DNIII">''[[Dark Nest III: The Swarm War]]''</ref>

Near the end of the [[Second Galactic Civil War]], Nickel One was [[Battle of Roche|attacked]] by the [[Imperial Remnant]] faction loyal to [[Darth Caedus]], and was defended by [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians]], who had established a base on the asteroid after an agreement with the Verpine.<ref name="I">''[[Legacy of the Force: Invincible]]''</ref>

